                               boolean collectConcreteDomains,
                               boolean collectInferredComponents,
                               boolean collectFullySpecifiedNames,
                               java.util.Set<java.lang.String> excludedModules)
        Creates a taxonomy builder instance.
        Parameters:
        searcher - - an active revision searcher on a branch where this reasoner taxonomy builder should collect data from
        collectConcreteDomains - - if concrete domain reference set members should be populated
        collectInferredComponents - - if the inferred counterparts of collected components should also be collected
        collectFullySpecifiedNames - - if an active FSN for each participating active concepts should also be collected
        excludedModules - - the set of modules to exclude from classification
